{"tid":1770637,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[代 post] 我地係一班熱愛公義嘅香港人","createTime":"2019-12-05T10:26:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T10:51:54.000Z","uid":222614,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ce928f41956c2d08d8aefa842e854e405e8941","tid":1770637,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:26:39.000Z","msg":"我地係一班熱愛公義嘅香港人。 鑑於香港公民今普遍對特區政府屬下之警隊極不信任，因此成立左一個調查團隊。希望透過一個公開嘅平台將調查真相之權力還於公眾。<br />\n<br />\n對於過去接連嘅不尋常命案，我地感到非常痛心及㥬惶。我地一直期望警隊內尚存有良心之士，可以運用手上嘅權力去還原真相，但結果卻係令人失望。大部份命案不但沉冤未雪，而且被警方一句「無可疑」就草草了事，真相被越埋越深，兇手逍遙法外，究竟警隊入面發生左咩事？香港人畀警隊嘅資源用在何處？在香港，人命何價？<br />\n<br />\n我地誠然等唔切警方嘅改變，於是決定用私人時間去籌備調查組。我地目的係要將調查權交還公眾，因為警方似乎已經放棄左佢地呢一部份嘅職責。我地希望公眾可以積極參與，為每宗懸案提供線索。<br />\n<br />\n我地運用名為 Git 嘅檔案管理技術去管理資料，透過公開平台 GitLab 去討論，整理及公佈結果。每位香港人都可以開設 GitLab User Account 參與調查工作。<br />\n<br />\nCitizens' Investigation Services<br />\n民間調查服務組<br />\n<a href=\"https://gitlab.com/hkcis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgitlab.com%2Fhkcis&d=6rVCxxaC9rfKwEt%2B83BPWJWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=2138208d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gitlab.com/hkcis</a><br />\n<br />\n關於我地<br />\n<a href=\"https://gitlab.com/hkcis/about-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgitlab.com%2Fhkcis%2Fabout-us&d=6rVCxxaC9rfKwEt%2B83BPWJWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=d3412faf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gitlab.com/hkcis/about-us</a><br />\n<br />\n我地現正收集懸案<br />\n<a href=\"https://gitlab.com/hkcis/list-of-unsolved-cases\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgitlab.com%2Fhkcis%2Flist-of-unsolved-cases&d=6rVCxxaC9rfKwEt%2B83BPWJWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=ceec318a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gitlab.com/hkcis/list-of-unsolved-cases</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，我地將會對某幾宗警方認為無可疑嘅案件首先進行調查。我地會陸續開「Project」並且更新進度。大家可以留意我地嘅專頁 <a href=\"https://gitlab.com/hkcis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgitlab.com%2Fhkcis&d=6rVCxxaC9rfKwEt%2B83BPWJWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=2138208d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gitlab.com/hkcis</a><br />\n<br />\n多謝各位"},{"pid":"b255c34a25e3d54dcb1fd6dad1557ddffd6c3b73","tid":1770637,"uid":35155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:28:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a0f4517da1b01e6c6108d974be78e0491ef74a8","tid":1770637,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:29:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dc9834d18febd4c57ca14e58547afb759555a54b","tid":1770637,"uid":92247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:30:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>連登已經報廢！行動post打春袋冇人推！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n【不・推爆行動post!!!】和理非12.7 Family Day一於遊車河玩春袋!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1762530\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1762530</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"826d10d4042699997f11004522d2b00f3ec3ee9b","tid":1770637,"uid":229955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:30:24.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c579d08cfc2d0b4271f4e07779e49927e352eeb","tid":1770637,"uid":45558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c673898c58d57605b67c4d975652dfec822af123","tid":1770637,"uid":83072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:31:53.000Z","msg":"128維園見"},{"pid":"8cb5c709a550ae5be8b4124d586dcadc3a44bbc9","tid":1770637,"uid":304160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:32:34.000Z","msg":"推 正"},{"pid":"f5c4ed3526ba22d8589e899bda8d4f3cde262f82","tid":1770637,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T10:34:25.000Z","msg